<div role=3D"note" class=3D"hatnote navigation-not-searchable">This article=
 is about the statistical precision of estimates from sample surveys. For o=
bservational errors, see <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Observati=
onal_error" title=3D"Observational error">Observational error</a>. For safe=
ty margins in engineering, see <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fac=
tor_of_safety" title=3D"Factor of safety">Factor of safety</a>. For toleran=
ce in engineering, see <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Engineering=
_tolerance" title=3D"Engineering tolerance">Engineering tolerance</a>. For =
the eponymous movie, see <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Margin_fo=
r_error_(film)" class=3D"mw-redirect" title=3D"Margin for error (film)">Mar=
gin for error (film)</a>.</div>
